{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_ZSBwG09bkoX18ziIqxsjduPe","type":"tool_result","content":" FAQs – Focus Bear Questions Answered html { overflow-y: scroll; } body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; } /* Size-adjust fallback fonts to match real fonts */ @font-face { font-family: 'Inter'; font-display: swap; } @font-face { font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-display: swap; } Features Pricing FAQ Science Blog Contact Search Get the App ✕ Close Focus Bear for Desktop Download for Mac Version 3.32.484 Download for Windows Version 3.0.207 Download for Android ionicons-v5_logos Download for iOS .cls-1{fill:#223244;}.cls-2{fill:#b7b7b7;}.cls-3{fill:#ffffff;}.cls-4{fill:#ffc861;}.cls-5{fill:#bf9649;}.cls-6{fill:#fff4df;}.cls-7,.cls-9{fill:none;stroke:#000;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}.cls-7{stroke-width:6.18px;}.cls-8{fill:#000;}.cls-9{stroke-width:6px;} We&#x27;re working on the Android App . In the meantime you can signup for the waitlist and we&#x27;ll email you as soon as it&#x27;s ready for download. I consent to providing my email and accept the Privacy Policy of Focus Bear Thank you! Your submission has been received! Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form. Also available for other platforms: Download for Mac Download for Windows Download for Android ionicons-v5_logos Download for iOS Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) About the App Pricing About ADHD What platforms does Focus Bear run on? Focus Bear is available for Mac, Windows, Android and iOS. Can I use Focus Bear on multiple devices? Focus Bear features a secure cloud sync design, so you can keep your data and focus modes synced between devices. How do I get support? Send us message through the contact page , or start a chat with one of our support team members by clicking on the chat icon on the lower left side. Does the app log my keystrokes and take screenshots? No. The only thing we log is information you provide at the end of a Focus Block (what did you achieve/what were the distractions?) and when you use our quantified self feature (how many pushups did you do?). Will the app interrupt me when I&#x27;m in a meeting? Valid concern. If you’ve used other apps like Focus Bear, you’ve probably had them interrupt you at inappropriate times (e.g. when you’re on a video call) or be very inflexible with blocking.We’ve done our best to use the best aspects of nudge theory (i.e. a slight amount of friction will move you towards your goals) without being annoying. Focus Bear is smart enough to not pop up during video calls.We have two modes: “cuddly bear” mode and “grizzly bear” mode. In “cuddly bear” mode, it is very easy to remove app blocks and postpone breaks. In “grizzly bear” mode, you have to wait a while before you can deactivate blocks.Cuddly Bear mode is the default and you should only activate grizzly bear mode if you really want extra support. Will it interfere with Do Not Disturb mode? No, it will not interfere with Do Not Disturb mode. How frequently will it make me take breaks? By default, the app will make you take breaks every 20 minutes. You can always adjust this interval to your preference in the app settings. Why is it good for people with ADHD? Having an app that enforces morning and evening routines, regular breaks, and focus modes is beneficial for individuals with ADHD as it provides structure, reduces distractions, and promotes time management and productivity. Focus Bear offers reminders, accountability, and customizable features that help individuals establish consistent routines, stay focused, and take necessary breaks. It increases self-awareness, supports better organization, and fosters a sense of accomplishment, ultimately improving overall well-being and symptom management for those with ADHD. How does Focus Bear work? Built by a team with ADHD, Focus Bear is based on neuroscience principles to help you stick with your habits and get stuff done. Click here to read more. Can I use Focus Bear for free? Focus Bear is free to use for Basic Features. How much does it cost? By upgrading to Pro","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7306cb3-f577-448d-82ba-7c9e9ee47b08","uuid":"5c4e21d2-2872-4263-a0e0-68cbd513edaf","timestamp":"2026-05-21T17:39:31.340Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":" FAQs – Focus Bear Questions Answered html { overflow-y: scroll; } body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; } /* Size-adjust fallback fonts to match real fonts */ @font-face { font-family: 'Inter'; font-display: swap; } @font-face { font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-display: swap; } Features Pricing FAQ Science Blog Contact Search Get the App ✕ Close Focus Bear for Desktop Download for Mac Version 3.32.484 Download for Windows Version 3.0.207 Download for Android ionicons-v5_logos Download for iOS .cls-1{fill:#223244;}.cls-2{fill:#b7b7b7;}.cls-3{fill:#ffffff;}.cls-4{fill:#ffc861;}.cls-5{fill:#bf9649;}.cls-6{fill:#fff4df;}.cls-7,.cls-9{fill:none;stroke:#000;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}.cls-7{stroke-width:6.18px;}.cls-8{fill:#000;}.cls-9{stroke-width:6px;} We&#x27;re working on the Android App . In the meantime you can signup for the waitlist and we&#x27;ll email you as soon as it&#x27;s ready for download. I consent to providing my email and accept the Privacy Policy of Focus Bear Thank you! Your submission has been received! Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form. Also available for other platforms: Download for Mac Download for Windows Download for Android ionicons-v5_logos Download for iOS Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) About the App Pricing About ADHD What platforms does Focus Bear run on? Focus Bear is available for Mac, Windows, Android and iOS. Can I use Focus Bear on multiple devices? Focus Bear features a secure cloud sync design, so you can keep your data and focus modes synced between devices. How do I get support? Send us message through the contact page , or start a chat with one of our support team members by clicking on the chat icon on the lower left side. Does the app log my keystrokes and take screenshots? No. The only thing we log is information you provide at the end of a Focus Block (what did you achieve/what were the distractions?) and when you use our quantified self feature (how many pushups did you do?). Will the app interrupt me when I&#x27;m in a meeting? Valid concern. If you’ve used other apps like Focus Bear, you’ve probably had them interrupt you at inappropriate times (e.g. when you’re on a video call) or be very inflexible with blocking.We’ve done our best to use the best aspects of nudge theory (i.e. a slight amount of friction will move you towards your goals) without being annoying. Focus Bear is smart enough to not pop up during video calls.We have two modes: “cuddly bear” mode and “grizzly bear” mode. In “cuddly bear” mode, it is very easy to remove app blocks and postpone breaks. In “grizzly bear” mode, you have to wait a while before you can deactivate blocks.Cuddly Bear mode is the default and you should only activate grizzly bear mode if you really want extra support. Will it interfere with Do Not Disturb mode? No, it will not interfere with Do Not Disturb mode. How frequently will it make me take breaks? By default, the app will make you take breaks every 20 minutes. You can always adjust this interval to your preference in the app settings. Why is it good for people with ADHD? Having an app that enforces morning and evening routines, regular breaks, and focus modes is beneficial for individuals with ADHD as it provides structure, reduces distractions, and promotes time management and productivity. Focus Bear offers reminders, accountability, and customizable features that help individuals establish consistent routines, stay focused, and take necessary breaks. It increases self-awareness, supports better organization, and fosters a sense of accomplishment, ultimately improving overall well-being