nce challenges: Distractions from social media, entertainment sites and messaging services make it harder than ever to stay focused. Difficulties in detaching from hyper-focused states cause poor punctuality, poor deadline adherence and many other physical and mental health issues that impact productivity such as muscular pain, difficulties","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
